27FCB7D0.Line7.6D03F: Meshif. Don’t move. Don’t speak to anyone. There is great danger lurking here.

296DE5C3.Line27.8CA44: It must hold some treasure, eh?

63419FFA.VoiceDir3.8CA44: Intrigued by this hidden gem in the desert

8F54F740.Line25.6D03F: A relic from the days of old Kehjistan maybe. Lost to time until Elias seized it.

DF8B230D.VoiceDir25.6D03F: Musing on what this could be--not excited like Meshif. More suspicious and cautious.

F43839CD.Line3.8CA44: Look at this! To think such an intriguing place was hidden beyond the storm.

F584F2BF.Line23.8CA44: You've grown fearful in your old age, my friend! But worry not, I will stay put.
